      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pamette wiſſu/ \nkas tam peederreja appakſch \nJahſepa Rohkas/ un wiꞥſch ne \ngahdaja lihds ar to ne mas/ ſa \nween par to Maisi/ ko wiꞥſch eh- \nde: Un Jahſeps bija raschens/un \ntam bij fkaiſts Gihmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke/pehz Schahm \nLeetahu mette winna Kunga \nSeewa farwas Azziſ us Jahſe- \npu/ un fazziſa: gull pee mannis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥſchleedeſehß/ un faz- \nzija us farwa Kunga Seewu: \nRaugi/ mans Kungs ne gahda \npar ne ka/ kas Namnā irr/ un \nwiff/ kas winnam peederr/ irr \nwiꞥſch mannā Rohkā dewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne kas irr ſchinnt Namntā \nleelaks pahr mannim/ un wiꞥſch \nman ne maſ irr atſleedsis/ bes \ntew ween/ tapehz/ ka tu wiſna \nSeewa effi/ ka tad man buhs \ntahdu leelu Launu padarriht/ \nun prett Deewu apgrehkoteeß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad winna ifDeenas \nſcho uhs Jahſepu runnaja/ un \ntas wiſnai ne paklausfija/ ka tas \nbuhtu pee winnas gulſejis/ jeb \nkahtt winnas bijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad notikke tas Jahſe- \npaim tahdā Deena Namnā nah- \nfoht/ farwu Darbu padarriht/ \nun ne weenam no teem Namna- \nLaudim Mahjās effoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fagrahbe ta wiſnau\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu ta redſeja/ \nfawas Drehbes wiſnas \nbij pamettis/ un ahra iſ\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fafanze ta \nNamna-Sainni/ un run \nteem/ un fazziſa: Ra \nwiſch irr to Eebrēisku W \nmuns weddis muhs a \ntas nahze pee man gull \nes brehzu wiſſā Galwā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tas dsirdej \nfawu Balfi pazehlu un \ntad pamette tas farwas \npee man/ un behdse nohſ \nmanzahs ahra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta likke wiſſa \nbes pee ſewim klaht/ kam \nna Kungs pahrnahze/ \nnaja ta us wiſnu/ peh \nWahrdeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fazziſa: Tas \nkis Kalps/ ko tu mumē \ndis effi/ nahze pee man \napſimeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad es farwu \nzehtu un brehzu/ tad pa \nfawas Drehbes pee man \nun isbehdse ahra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad wiſna k \nwas Seewas Wahrdū \nja/ ka ta us wiſnu bij \nfi/ fazzidama: Ta un t \ntaifs Kalps darrījis/ ta \ntahs winna Kungs duſin\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahſepa Kun\n"
    }
  ],
